Class BaseErrorDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwthaachen.openlap.visualizer.core.dtos.error.BaseErrorDTO

  • public class BaseErrorDTO
extends Object
    A base class which represents the model(contents) of the error that will be sent back to the client. For further modifications inherit from this class.
